Pysymo
======

+ -1) CR/LF in source files - shebang string doesn't work on Linux
+ 0) JSON parse and error strings (special symbols and \escape)
+ 1) Pagination
+ 2) Charts - types, cache data
3) Script to remove old data from db - older 1 month (configurable) or TTL-collection
4) Tail button with autorefresh
+ 5) Config file for tools scripts
+ 6) Indexes
+ 7) Usable statistics (db stat - size, messages count)
8) Error logging: HTTP 404/500, python exception, 'no module named ...'
9) Hard limit of selected documents: about 1000-3000 documents
10) Login with Flask-Login